data.description: Great value in this 4 bedroom 2 full bath cape on nearly 1 1/2 acres. Some TLC needed. Close by October 31, 2011 and receive up to 3.5% of the final sales price to be used for closing cost assistance. For Primary home buyers only. This is a Fannie Mae Home Path property. Only primary home owners' offers will be considered during the first 15 days the listing is active. No offer will be considered during the 1st 3 days on the market. Any and all costs associated with buyers lenders appraisal to include any necessary repairs will be paid for by the buyer and Not the seller.
